    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "For insights on ongoing conversations on these topics see the “Food, Waste, and Sustainability: Synergizing Ontology Efforts” workshop at ICBO2025 https://sites.google.com/view/fws2025workshop/home-page"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#seeAlso" : [ {
    "@id" : "https://www.w3id.org/climoo/climoo-plastico#ClimOO_0000175"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#annotatedProperty" : [ {
    "@id" : "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#annotatedSource" : [ {
    "@id" : "https://www.w3id.org/climoo/climoo-plastico#ClimOO_0000178"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#annotatedTarget" : [ {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "Currently, the ClimOO Ontology imports EnvO representation of waste role and includes a class for plastic upcycling. This is adequate for current ontology purposes. Given the strict interconnection between upcycling and recycling processes, however, we envision discussions with subject matter expert for possible implementations."
  } ]
