  "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115" : [ {
    "@value" : "x simultaneous with y iff ω(x) = ω(y) and ω(α ) = ω(α), where α is a function that maps a process to a start point, and ω is a function that maps a process to an end point and '=' indicates the same instance in time."
  } ],
